w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/colman-domingo-joe-jackson@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/colman-domingo-joe-jackson@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/colman-domingo-joe-jackson@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>科尔曼·多明戈在一部<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-when-the-michael-jackson-biopic-is-coming-out-3570534">即将上映的流行音乐之王传记片中</a>饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-jackson">迈克尔·杰克逊</a>的父亲乔·杰克逊。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944">生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/colman-domingo-michael-jackson-father-joe-biopic-1235887187/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，多明戈将在即将上映的电影中饰演乔·杰克逊，搭档是迈克尔的侄子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-when-the-michael-jackson-biopic-is-coming-out-3570534">贾法尔和 9 岁的朱利亚诺·克鲁·瓦尔迪，两人将分别饰演成人版和儿童版的迈克尔</a>。</p><p>多明戈通过<em>Variety</em>谈到他的选角：“与贾法尔合作真是令人兴奋。杰梅因·杰克逊的儿子扮演迈克尔，他令人惊叹，我认为制片人格雷厄姆·金组建了一个令人难以置信的演员阵容。” </p><figure id="attachment_3564067" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564067" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564067" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023.jpg" alt="科尔曼·多明戈" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/colman_domingo_2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564067" class="wp-caption-text">科尔曼·多明戈。 （格雷格·德奎尔/Variety via Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>他补充道：“我很高兴能成为一部探索传奇人物迈克尔·杰克逊复杂灵魂以及他作为全球偶像对音乐和文化的影响的电影的一部分。我不仅很幸运能够扮演乔·杰克逊这个丰富、复杂且有缺陷的角色，而且我还可以坐在前排欣赏贾法尔令人难以置信的转变。”</p><p>据制作公司狮门影业证实，这部即将上映的传记片名为<em>《迈克尔》</em> ，已确认将于 2025 年 4 月 18 日在美国上映。</p><p> <i>《迈克尔》</i>将由安托万·福卡 (Antoine Fuqua) 执导，他因拍摄<i>《训练日》</i> 、 <i>《均衡器》</i>和<i>《布鲁克林最佳》</i>等电影而闻名。该书也将由约翰·洛根撰写，他之前曾为《<i>角斗士》</i> 、 <i>《飞行者》</i> 、《007：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/skyfall-reviewed-758898"><i>天幕杀机</i></a>》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-16306-309465#:~:text=Following%20his%20own%20Skyfall%2C%20he,to%20go%20on%20a%20bit."><i>007：幽灵》</i></a>等电影撰写剧本。 </p><figure id="attachment_3570536" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3570536" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3570536" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024.jpg" alt="迈克尔杰克逊" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/michael_jackson_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3570536" class="wp-caption-text">迈克尔·杰克逊（Kevin Mazur/WireImage 摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在迈克尔·杰克逊的其他新闻中，十二月，宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-jacksons-first-ever-studio-recording-to-be-released-3554540">杰克逊第一次录音室录音的音频将作为限量版包的一部分发布</a>。</p><p>这张唱片录制于 56 年前，当时杰克逊只有 9 岁，第一次和他的兄弟们一起进入芝加哥的 One-derful 录音室。在 1967 年 7 月 13 日举行的会议中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-jackson-five">杰克逊五人</a>组制作了一首名为“Big Boy”的歌曲，并已证实这是这位标志性歌手的声音第一次被录入磁带。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/colman-domingo-cast-as-joe-jackson-in-michael-jackson-biopic-3577421">科尔曼·多明戈 (Colman Domingo) 在迈克尔·杰克逊 (Michael Jackson) 传记片中饰演乔·杰克逊 (Joe Jackson) 后</a>，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上播出。</p> ;
韩国流行偶像在已故 ASTRO 歌手 Moonbin 生日之际向他致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/k-pop-idols-pay-tribute-astro-moonbin-26th-birthday-3577405?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=k-pop-idols-pay-tribute- astro-文彬-26岁生日Gladys YeoFri, 26 Jan 2024 04:48:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3577405 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="astro 文彬 银优 十七岁的 woozi" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手今天就满26岁了</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/k-pop-idols-pay-tribute-astro-moonbin-26th-birthday-3577405">韩国流行偶像在已故 ASTRO 歌手 Moonbin 生日之际向他致敬，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="astro 文彬 银优 十七岁的 woozi" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/astro-moonbin-cha-eunwoo-seventeen-woozi-260124-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cha-eun-woo">车银优</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">SEVENTEEN</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/woozi">Woozi</a>在内的多位韩国流行音乐艺术家在已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/astro">ASTRO</a>歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/moonbin">文彬</a>的生日当天为他献上了祝福。</p><p>去年4月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/astro-moonbin-dead-3432736">ASTRO成员文彬在首尔江南区的家中去世，享年25岁</a>。今天（1月26日）是这位歌手的26岁生日。为了纪念他的生日，他的 ASTRO 乐队成员以及其他几位偶像分享了生日祝福和歌曲奉献。</p><p>车银优在该团体的官方 YouTube 频道上发布了美国 DJ 组合 SLANDER 的歌曲《Love Is Gone》的翻唱作品。此前，他在去世一个月后发行了另一张10cm的《Stalker》封面，献给Moonbin。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[封面] 爱已消失 (SLANDER) l 演唱者：车银优" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/X9ein7zEwLE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.sportskeeda.com/pop-culture/news-i-will-never-forget-smile-filled-love-seventeen-s-woozi-dedicates-what-kind-future-astro-s-moonbin-birthday" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SEVENTEEN</em></a>歌手兼制作人 Woozi 发行了一首名为《What Kind of Future》的原创歌曲，他于 2018 年在一场音乐会上首次表演。我永远不会忘记你充满爱的笑容。”</p><p>在 Woozi 去世后致文彬的一封信中，他表示这位歌手很喜欢这首歌，并敦促他发行这首歌。在同一封信中，他承诺在文彬生日那天为他发行这本书。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：什么样的未来" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/1S46HO8uCleN4pov8D3bGL?si=JOniAJmMQkK5_aJIzZ_QqA&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>在X（原Twitter）上，ASTRO成员MJ和JinJin也分享了他们对文彬的生日祝福。 “我的一生都以为你在注视着我。你吃得好，休息得好，对吧？”金金写道。 “今天一定要吃海带汤。我们的照片不多，我应该多拍一些。今天你一定比任何人都快乐。我爱你兄弟。”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ko" dir="ltr"> 우리 빈다 생일 축하한다 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f49c.png" alt="💜" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br /> 사랑하고 보고 싶다 내 동생^^<br /> 글쓴 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%95%84%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%9C?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">기문</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%95%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%95%98?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">빈</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%98%81%EC%9B%90%ED%95%9C_%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%EB%8B%AC_%EB%AC%B8%EB%B9%88_%EC%83%9D%EC%9D%BC%EC%B6%95%ED%95%98%ED%95%B4?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">_생일축하해</a> <a href="https://t.co/Lh3b97Sp7l">pic.twitter.com/Lh3b97Sp7l</a></p><p> — ASTRO 아스트로 (@offclASTRO) <a href="https://twitter.com/offclASTRO/status/1750534094331711670?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ko" dir="ltr"> 빈아 생일 축하한다！！ㅎㅎ잘 지내지?? 오늘은 더 보고 싶은 날다!!<br /> 형 요즘 아주 열심히 살고 있어!! 보고 있을 거라 생각하며 산다 ㅎㅎ 잘 먹고 잘 쉬고 있지？ 오늘은 미역국 꼭 챙겨 먹고 우리 사진 Been 많 없네 사진 좀 많 찍어둘걸 그랬다ㅎㅎ누구보다 행복한 하루 보내야 한다 사랑한다 내… <a href="https://t.co/KNR1p8tx4y">pic.twitter.com/KNR1p8tx4y</a></p><p> — ASTRO 아스트로 (@offclASTRO) <a href="https://twitter.com/offclASTRO/status/1750534867807563951?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 1 月 25 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> ASTRO 的尹山河、SEVENTEEN 的 DK 和 Seungkwan 也在他们的 Instagram 故事中分享了对这位歌手的致敬。与 Moonbin 同一天生日的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/monsta-x">MO