24 年盛大节日感到非常兴奋，每年这个节日都变得越来越大、越来越好。我们已经拥有了出色的音乐阵容，还有更多的内容有待宣布。这是与朋友、家人一起度过八月银行假日周末的理想方式，并为每个人提供丰富的娱乐活动。大家农场见。”</p><p>其他即将在音乐节上表演的音乐表演——包括周六晚上的头条新闻——以及客座厨师和家庭娱乐的完整阵容将很快公布。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-and-anne-marie-to-headline-alex-james-big-feastival-3158682">2022 年的盛大节日</a>以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stereophonics">立体声、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-marie">安妮玛丽</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-human-league">人类联盟</a>为头条新闻。特邀嘉宾<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a>也在科茨沃尔德农场进行了表演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">阿尔菲·坦普尔曼</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-futureheads">The Futureheads</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-sherlocks">The Sherlocks</a> 、 <a href="/artists/the-lottery-winners">The Lottery Winners</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lola-young">Lola</a> Young、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-bugg">Jake Bugg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gabrielle">Gabrielle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-ryder">Sam Ryder、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/basement-jaxx">Basement Jaxx</a>也在整个周末亮相。</p><p>其他新闻方面，贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382">获得了全英舞蹈表演奖提名</a>。她还将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-and-disclosure-to-headline-parklife-festival-2024-lineup-announced-3575349">Parklife Festival 2024</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stormzy-chase-status-becky-hill-lead-boardmasters-2024-line-up-3551298">Boardmasters</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/limp-bizkit-and-richard-ashcroft-announce-2024-margate-dreamland-shows-3553227">Margate Dreamland</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victorious-festival-announces-headliners-for-2024-buy-tickets-3553549">Victorious 音乐节上</a>表演。</p><p> Snow Patrol 还将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victorious-festival-announces-headliners-for-2024-buy-tickets-3553549">Victorious 音乐节</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-jamie-t-snow-patrol-and-more-for-y-not-2024-3576409">Y Not</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paulo-nutini-jamie-t-and-snow-patrol-lead-stacked-tramlines-2024-line-up-buy-tickets-3576202">Tramlines</a>上演出。</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/becky-hill-and-snow-patrol-lead-line-up-for-alex-james-big-feastival-2024-3577143">贝基·希尔 (Becky Hill) 和雪地巡逻队 (Snow Patrol) 在亚历克斯·詹姆斯 (Alex James) 的 Big Feastival 2024 上领衔主演的阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
